{"type": "article", "id": 20419, "title": "野餐工具箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-08T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122338BYcgt2zZKMhN7TSP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款木质的方盒子像一个野餐盒，它其实是一个工具箱，巧妙地融入了各种厨房小工具。盒子的盖子是一块砧板，里整齐放置了打蛋器和各类刮刀，他们都配套设计了木质把手，颜色统一，可以错位放置，显得简洁干净。当一群人出去野餐时就可以带着它，每人分得一个工具，利于促进合作。<a href=\"http://www.andyiliao.com/#/uncontained/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122334foW3BAOL12TMIbH4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122334rl5qS0BfGwPUEpjm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.04666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122335fXdasB8omxPiL3tF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071223369aN8zv3hXBQbH4LT.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}